  "title": "Dark Grilled Algerian Date Skewers",
  "description": "Bitter and snappy solo dinner dish from Algeria featuring medjool dates, fry grind rice khao khu, and a blend of Mediterranean spices, grilled to perfection on a raclette grill.",
