  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the raclette grill to medium high heat.",
    "Thread 2-3 pitted medjool dates onto each skewer.",
    "In a small bowl, mix together fry grind rice khao khu, olive oil, lemon juice, smoked paprika, ground cumin, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Brush the mixture evenly onto both sides of the date skewers.",
    "Place the skewers on the preheated raclette grill and cook for 2-3 minutes per side, or until the dates are caramelized and slightly charred.",
    "Remove the skewers from the grill and sprinkle with chopped fresh parsley.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy.",
    "Repeat the process until all the ingredients are used up."
